- **`build/installer.nsh` ‚Äî `customUnInstall` updated** ‚Äî Removes both the new bundle-id folders (`com.bloomx.freexan.link`, `com.bloomx.freexan.audio`, `com.bloomx.misterbloomx`, `com.aescripts.submachine`) and the legacy folder-name copies (`Link_freeXan`, `Audio_freeXan`, `MisterBloomX`, `SubMachine`) so an uninstall from any freeXan version cleans up fully.

