## [v2.9.14] ‚Äî 2026-06-09

### Fix ¬∑ Audio ¬∑ CEP
- **Dummy duration always 1 sec when no trim set** ‚Äî `requestDummyFile()` used `trimEnd` directly; since `trimEnd` initialises to `0`, `isNaN(0)=false` so `end=0`, giving `dur=0` which fell back to `1`. Fixed: guard `trimEnd > 0`; fall back to `wavesurfer.getDuration() || selectedAudioRawDuration || selectedAudio.duration`. (`cep-extension/audio.js`)
